heroInfo.introduction: Full Stack Developer,Machine Learning Enthusiast,React Native App Developer
heroInfo.description: I'm a Full Stack Developer with experience in both web and mobile development, passionate about building intelligent systems using Machine Learning. I also develop cross-platform mobile apps using React Native.

projects.headline1: Developed a web application to track income and expenses with secure user authentication.
projects.headline2: Users can add, categorize, and manage expenses and income entries.Integrated a circular (pie) chart to help users visualize spending patterns effectively.

projects.headline1: Developed a travel itinerary recommendation system that generates personalized plans based on origin, destination, number of days, and budget, leveraging the Gemini API for travel suggestions.
projects.headline2: Built a React.js frontend integrated with Firebase for secure database storage, enabling users to create, view, and manage their travel itineraries seamlessly.

projects.projectName: AI-Driven Career & Financial Planning in STEM
projects.headline1: Built a React-based application that showcases career path information, including job titles, salary expectations, growth opportunities, and personalized financial goals.
projects.headline2: Integrated PDF generation to allow users to download a detailed career plan, including sections for savings targets, investment strategies, and expert advice.
